# Installation

1. Install [TamperMonkey](https://www.notion.so/1377f609618641b9af50a77f7a3e2daa)
2. Click to open extension > Click Dashboard
3. Open Utilities section
    1. Copy text [https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nchicong/userscripts/master/gmail-web-shortcuts.js](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nchicong/userscripts/master/gmail-web-shortcuts.js)
    2. Scroll to the bottom of Utilities section, locate **Import from URL** field
    3. Paste and click Install
4. To check if the script is enabled and injected at the right site, open Gmail and see if the script is listed when clicking the extension button
